      "date": "2013-08-03 03:28:06.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/90d23e6c-fbe4-11e2-aaad-52540035b04c).  Ran 3 tests.  2 tests failed: sanity, sanity.",
