      "date": "2013-08-06 06:55:05.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/6e4b6a00-fe58-11e2-92b1-52540035b04c).  Ran 6 tests.  2 tests failed: sanity, sanity.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
